\SE[29]Ugh, I've been through a tough time.... It feels like
Luna's pervertedness has increased over time.... \SE[60]It's not
good that the rules are increasing....

\SE[42]But... it's true that I felt my heart racing....

too.... \SE[48]Hmm... What should I do...?

\SE[52]No, accepting my partner's sexual preferences is also a
weakness of being in love, a duty as someone who loves...!

\SE[5]... Oh, that's right. I have to prepare because tomorrow is
early. \SE[1] I don't want to be late and inconvenience everyone.
\SE[57]Okay, I'm ready. \SE[55]I'll go to bed early today...
